{"tid":2141394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周小龍 ： 網球總會會長莫君逸上星期違反限聚令與朋友打網球","createTime":"2020-08-05T15:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T16:10:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"067b9cb2e9e23e948d53613138df2e0f2f77ad2e","tid":2141394,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"2020年7月28號，當香港所有會所及公眾網球場已關閉，網球總會會長莫君逸Philip Mok［圖右］竟然搵到網球場打波😡佢不但冇幫自己業界嘅教練同球員發聲爭取網球場盡快重開，佢亦杯葛我琴日嘅 &ldquo;體育業界反政府一刀㧅&rdquo; 記者會。<br />\n<br />\n我喺呢度呼籲所有網球教練，球員，同埋投票俾佢選做會長嘅42間私人會所，大大發聲要求莫君逸Philip Mok幫業界爭取網球設施盡快重開。<br />\n<br />\n莫會長，網球場禁開，你仲有閑情打波？幫你嘅業界做啲嘢啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102410358166146/posts/150973056643209/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102410358166146%2Fposts%2F150973056643209%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=02cca034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102410358166146/posts/150973056643209/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fe19f379e8ea9ed16fcb10e9a1813157e1dd90b1","tid":2141394,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:38:55.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"55adb1d5535e15e55aa1bd2ed5d3597d12d7bb2d","tid":2141394,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲藍嘅仆街係要公審下"},{"pid":"2f2760d2551b10379c1764853da7e196f267cde1","tid":2141394,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"周小龍話有聯絡過網總會長講業界停業問題但會長唔理佢，呢位會長對業界真係有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd9e87d9c20fca37428fa6fa9f6107419cd1f58","tid":2141394,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T15:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"